videos.description: Deondre Francois pass complete to Auden Tate for 27 yds to the BC 24 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: D. Francois pass,to A. Tate for 27 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Florida State finishes off its opening possession with Deondre Francois hitting Auden Tate for the six-yard touchdown to give the Seminoles the early 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: Florida State strikes first with Francois's 6-yard TD pass

videos.description: Myles Willis run for 39 yds to the FlaSt 35 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: M. Willis run for 39 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Florida State makes it two-for-two finding the end zone on both of their possessions, thanks to another Deondre Francois touchdown pass.
videos.headline: Francois tosses second TD pass of first quarter

videos.description: Active military officer is reunited with his family during the 2nd quarter
videos.headline: Active military officer is reunited with his family during the 2nd quarter

videos.description: Ryan Otto, Chief Military Officer III of the United States Army, runs onto the field to surprise his family at the Boston College-Florida State game after a video message was played for them.
videos.headline: Army officer surprises family at FSU game

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Army officer surprises family at FSU game) 2016/11/11

videos.description: Dalvin Cook has a gaping hole to run through and only needs to make one cut back to get through the rest of the defense to score from 19 yards out extending Florida State's lead to 21-0.
videos.headline: Cook slices through the defense for 19-yard TD

videos.description: Florida State head coach Jimbo Fisher on his defensive success in the first half
videos.headline: Florida State head coach Jimbo Fisher on his defensive success in the first half

videos.description: Dalvin Cook run for 30 yds to the FlaSt 38 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: D. Cook run for 29 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Travis Rudolph makes the catch and is able to stay in bounds and dive over the pylon for the touchdown extending Florida State's lead to 28-0.
videos.headline: Rudolph toes the side line to get in the end zone

videos.description: Deondre Francois pass complete to Auden Tate for 22 yds to the BC 44 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Great catch by Auden Tate for a 22 yard gain and a 1st down

videos.description: Sean Maguire pass complete to Auden Tate for 28 yds to the BC 6 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Auden Tate makes another great catch for a gain of 28 down to the Boston College 6 yard line

videos.description: Even with Sean Maguire in at quarterback, Florida State keeps scoring as he finds Auden Tate for a six-yard touchdown to put the Seminoles up 35-0.
videos.headline: Florida State pouring it on with Tate's second TD

videos.description: Patrick Towles sacked by Brian Burns and DeMarcus Walker for a loss of 5 yards to the BC 20
videos.headline: P. Towles sacked by B. Burns and D. Walker for -5 yds

videos.description: Florida State head coach Jimbo Fisher gives an update on Quarterback Deondre Francois's shoulder injury and why he pulled Dalvin Cook from the game
videos.headline: Fisher says Francois' injury not serious

videos.description: Florida State running back Dalvin Cook on approaching the record for most rushing yards in school history
videos.headline: Florida State running back Dalvin Cook on approaching the record for most rushing yards in school history
